creator: Arena Fitness Training Center
descriptionHtml: The Arena Coach app is designed for clients of trainers who have enrolled in the Arena Coach program. The app will send push notifications and prompt clients to answer yes/no question in regards to comply with healthy habits sent by the trainer.  Clients and trainers can track progress and help the client to improve overall health.
descriptionShort: The app is designed for clients of Arena Coach.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- workout design update with theme colors!
- you can now see your performance for an exercise on that day without looking at your history
- minor bug and speed improvements :)
